1. The Trump administration is considering a measure that would allow tariffs of up to 15% for 150 days;
2. Metaplanet CEO: Bitcoin will rise to $1 million;
3. According to on-chain data, James Wynn once again reduced his BTC long position to 1,687, and the liquidation price was reduced to $104,600, with a current floating loss of nearly $5 million;
4. Michael Saylor: The more places that accept Bitcoin, the more likely humans will succeed;
5. Tether CEO: The company holds more than 100,000 Bitcoins and 50 tons of gold;
6. The US SEC clarified that some PoS staking activities do not constitute securities transactions;
7. Paris Saint-Germain Football Club announced that it has included Bitcoin in its financial reserves;
8. The US SEC applied to the court to withdraw the lawsuit against Binance;
9. WalletConnect: Solana mobile phone will participate in the Solana ecosystem WCT token airdrop claim plan.
